These things are considered cheating, punishment is removal or ban.

-multiplaying (having two characters at the same time in the game)
-not reporting bugs
-abusing bugs (Major punishments!)
-lagging/crashing the mud
-using a set of triggers that play for you while you are not active (robot)
-duplicating equipment/money
-to put spellwords/quests in public share
-somehow getting free exp/money
-making rooms or objects to start bugging
-sharing characters with other people
-making monsters not fight back (included in 'abusing bugs')
-lying / not telling the truth to wizards
-forcefielding area entrances

SEE ALSO: help pkilling
